y(t)=\int\limits _{-\infty}^{\infty}x_{1}(\tau)\irf(t-\tau)\,\tdc\tau+\int\limits _{-\infty}^{\infty}x_{2}(\tau)\irf(t-\tau)\,\tdc\tau+\cdots=y_{1}(t)+y_{2}(t)+y_{3}(t)+\cdots\]

